Package org.hibernate.testing.logger

Class Log4J2DelegatingLogger

java.lang.Object
org.jboss.logging.Logger
org.hibernate.testing.logger.Log4J2DelegatingLogger
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, org.jboss.logging.BasicLogger
public final class Log4J2DelegatingLogger extends org.jboss.logging.Logger
A Logger implementation which delegates to Log4J2 but makes it possible to test for events being logged (not logged).
